name: Morning Mass In The Five Winds Cathedral
description: Part of The Recursive Series a collection of digital arts inspired by the illustrations of the artist M.C.Escher and mystery noire TV shows from the early 20th century. A bizarre and surprising universe created using recursive algorithms in old photos and movie frames, generating a contemporary look from the past.  Artist: Luiz André Gama  Artist Official Website: www.luizandregama.com  Date of Creation: 2021 - Size: 3012×4000px
